title: Anyone travelling Hampshire to Vic Farm or Schofields soon?

posts.content: Eddie at Vic Farm wants another servo for his other bus, and Alan Schofield wants another one for the bus he's working on now, so is anyone passing my place (J5 off the M3) and heading to Vic Farm or Schofield's before the Stanford Hall / AGM weekend so those guys can crack on with their builds / save them some postage?

Jim - if anyone volunteers perhaps I can add my box for Eddie with yours...?

Mark

HI Jim
Im going up for the AGM spoke to Eddy this week to book some electric if they are all willing to wait till then i am more than happy to take
them.
Cheers Steve
I'm going to the AGM, just wondered if anyone was heading that way before then so they can get it quicker.
